rider s first issue did a review on a group of header and exhaust systems for the cbr six zero zero f two they also included as a side bar the ontario slip on the dyno showed an increase from stock of five bhp at the rear wheel eight five verses nine one buyer beware of outrageous claimed increases in horse power it may have been true in the past but not today at zero zero one nine nine one cbr six zero zero f two allen tobias technical email convex computer corp marketing tobias convex com three zero zero zero waterview parkway richardson tx seven five zero eight three this bike is awesome and i m fearless let s go jay gleason